[07 FAQ]

Smarter decisions start with clear answers.

How long does a typical project take?

It depends on the scope. A landing page might take 23 weeks, while a full branding and website package could take 610. Well give you a clear timeline before we begin.

What if I dont know exactly what I need?

No problem. Well help you figure it out. Whether its a quick call or a deeper discovery session, well guide you through it.

Can I request just one service?

Absolutely. You can book a single service or bundle multiplewhatever fits your goals and timeline.

How do payments work?

For projects, we usually split payments into 2 or 3 milestones. For monthly plans, billing is done upfront each month. Everything is clear and agreed upon before we start.

What if I need changes after a project ends?

We offer ongoing support, either through our monthly plan or as-needed add-ons. You wont be left hanging.
